# Rule 7: Execution Management & Portfolio Update Pipeline

**Version:** 3.0 (Complete Pipeline Specification)
**Date:** October 25, 2025
**Status:** ACTIVE - MANDATORY COMPLIANCE

---

## Overview

Rule 7 defines the **complete execution and portfolio update pipeline** from authorized trades through execution to portfolio state updates. This pipeline ensures **institutional-grade execution**, **transaction cost optimization**, and **accurate portfolio tracking**.

**Key Principle:** ALL execution operations are governed by **Rule 4 (Risk Authorization)** and flow through the **TradingEngine (HOW) → UnifiedExecutionEngine (ACTION) → Portfolio Update** sequence.

