## Component Responsibility Matrix (Phases 8-11)

| Phase | Component | Input | Output | Can Authorize? | Can Execute? | Can Update Positions? |
|-------|-----------|-------|--------|---------------|--------------|----------------------|
| **8** | TradingEngine | TradingAuthorization | ExecutionRequest | ❌ NO | ❌ NO | ❌ NO |
| **9** | UnifiedExecutionEngine | ExecutionRequest | ExecutionResult | ❌ NO | ✅ YES | ❌ NO |
| **10** | CentralRiskManager | ExecutionResult | PositionUpdate | ✅ YES | ❌ NO | ✅ YES (ONLY HERE) |
| **11** | AnalyticsManager | ExecutionResult | QualityMetrics | ❌ NO | ❌ NO | ❌ NO |

**KEY PRINCIPLE:** 
- Only UnifiedExecutionEngine can **execute** trades
- Only CentralRiskManager can **update positions**
- All other components are **read-only observers**

