## PROHIBITED Execution Patterns

❌ **Unauthorized Execution**: Cannot execute without valid RiskManager authorization (Rule 4)
❌ **Direct Position Updates**: Must update positions through RiskManager callbacks (Rule 4)
❌ **Algorithm Bypassing**: Cannot use algorithms not authorized by RiskManager
❌ **Risk Limit Violations**: Cannot exceed authorized quantities or time limits
❌ **Independent Operation**: Cannot operate without orchestrator registration (Rule 1)
❌ **Regime-Unaware Execution**: Must adapt execution to regime conditions (Rule 2)

